## .NET 9 Spesifik
- `MapStaticAssets()` > `UseStaticFiles()` (performans)
- LINQ `CountBy()`, `AggregateBy()` — allocation-free aggregation
- `System.Text.Json` schema export, customizable indentation
- Dynamic GC: server GC yerine otomatik adaptation
- Native AOT: startup hizi icin deger, cold-start serverless
- Aspire entegrasyonu: service discovery, health, telemetry

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| `async void` | `async Task` |
| `.Result` / `.Wait()` | `await` |
| Entity'yi API'dan return | DTO/projection |
| Service Locator | Constructor injection |
| Fat Controller | Thin controller + MediatR |
| Generic `catch(Exception)` | Spesifik exception + log |
| Loop icinde DB call | Batch query / Include |
| `DateTime.Now` | `IDateTimeProvider` (testability) |

